  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You touch a weapon and temporarily enchant it, transforming it into a magic weapon. Choose one of the following damage types: acid, cold, fire, lightning, or thunder. For the duration, the weapon has a +1 bonus to attack rolls and deals an extra 1d12 damage of the chosen type when it hits.</p><p><strong><em>At Higher Levels:</em></strong> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 5th or 6th level, the bonus to attack rolls increases to +2 and the extra damage increases to 2d12. When you use a spell slot of 7th level or higher, the bonus increases to +3 and the extra damage increases to 3d12.</p>",
